### 1. Admin Login (Obtain Admin Token)
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "AdminPassword123!"
}

> {% client.global.set("adminToken", response.body.data.tokens.accessToken); %}

### 2. List Orders (Admin)
GET {{protocol}}://{{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/admin/orders?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get Order Details (Admin)
GET {{protocol}}://{{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/admin/orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4. Create Product (Admin)
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin New Product",
  "description": "Created via API",
  "price": 100000,
  "variants": []
}

### 5. Update Order Status (Admin Flow)
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/admin/orders/{{orderId}}/shipments
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "waybill": "WAYBILL-123",
  "courierCode": "jne"
}
